{"tid":945460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【發現新大陸】原來江澤民時代大陸央視內部玩得咁癲","createTime":"2018-12-18T01:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T04:46:59.000Z","uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c036183e8e1790d39e6f48d012bd437140648a3","tid":945460,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kIROv-oBhVA?t=196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkIROv-oBhVA%3Ft%3D196&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b7f9c93e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kIROv-oBhVA?t=196</a><br />\n（配音扮江澤民講嘢）有一點我要特別提出一下，我非常喜歡中央電視台記者提問，他們真是暖瓶掛在大腿上&mdash;&mdash;水平比較高。讓問什麼就問什麼，不讓問什麼，打死他們也不問，比香港記者強多了。這才是由中國特色的社會主義新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e1PCx_usPQ4?t=752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe1PCx_usPQ4%3Ft%3D752&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1bb89a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e1PCx_usPQ4?t=752</a><br />\n這樣的夜晚，除了創造人類，我們還有什麼追求！我們曾經一忍再忍，如今已經忍無可忍。不在放蕩中變壞，就在沉默中變態！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e1PCx_usPQ4?t=1239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe1PCx_usPQ4%3Ft%3D1239&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=74a1788b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e1PCx_usPQ4?t=1239</a><br />\n歷史的經驗又一次告訴我們，春，從來不是叫出來的；春，是真刀真槍幹出來的！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ddc0b424a66098fb9ce3c773b9c49249ea04a3","tid":945460,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"歷史的經驗又一次告訴我們，春，從來不是叫出來的；春，是真刀真槍幹出來的！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪姐係叫春唔係用把口齋叫<br />\n係要用「刀槍」「幹」出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}